<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">I have to agree with the point that we got something we never had before.  We can't really complain.  Let's face it, new armour or not, we are by far the most enjoyable class to play.  <p>

You can't be a one dimemsional player and be effective as an enchanter.  You have to pre-plan your spells very well depending on the situation you will be in.  Do you load 2 stuns or 2 mezs or, or , or........<p>

Even at level 18 my enchanter makes tough fights easy for our group.  We are caster heavy so tanking is out of the question.  I can make mobs stop attacking... run away... join our side... etc...  It's a blast!!!  <p>

As enchanter you are the quarterback of the fight.  You have to read the defence and act accordingly.  <p>

John@MaximumGaming</font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="DDDDDD">
